annotationA: Jetlag, isoform A; Jetlag is an F-box protein that is a component of an SCF E3 ubiquitin ligase complex. It targets tim for degradation upon light exposure, and is essential for photic entrainment of the circadian clock
annotationB: 26S proteasome regulatory complex subunit p48B; Regulatory particle triple-A ATPase 1 is an AAA-type ATPase protein that forms part of the heterohexameric ATPase ring of the regulatory complex of the 26S proteasome
